<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.276441>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Lasioglossum (Evylaeus) bicornutum Murao, sp. nov. A – F: holotype, female. G – I: paratype, female. A: lateral habitus. B: lower face. C: mesoscutum. D: sculpture on mesoscutum. E: mesoscutellum. F: mesepisternum. G: labrum. H: propodeal dorsum. I: inner hind tibial spur. Scale bars: H, 0.25 mm; G, I, 0.2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/276441/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.276442>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. A, B: Lasioglossum (Evylaeus) bicornutum Murao, sp. nov. C, D: Lasioglossum (Evylaeus) silvicolum Murao, sp. nov. E, F: Lasioglossum (Evylaeus) latifacies Murao, sp. nov. A – F: holotypes, females. A, C, E: head in frontal view. B, D, F: first metasomal tergum (left half, sculpture; right half, hair pattern). Scale bar: 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/276442/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

